/**
 * Shared label set for /horoscope/[rashi] hub + daily/weekly/monthly
 * variants + HubClient/HoroscopeClient/RashiArticle.
 *
 * Authored locales: en, hi.
 * Gemini-translated overlay (mai/mr/ta/te/kn/gu/bn) lives in
 * `src/lib/constants/horoscope-labels-overlay.json`, generated by
 * `scripts/translate-horoscope-via-gemini.py`.
 *
 * High-leverage SEO: rashi × locale × daily/weekly/monthly =
 * 12 × 9 × 3 distinct H1+description pairs. Per-locale H1 templates
 * carry {NAME} (rashi name) + {WESTERN_NAME} + {RANGE} or {MONTH} or
 * {WEEKDAY},{DATE} placeholders.
 *
 * Resolution: AUTHORED[locale] → OVERLAY[locale] → AUTHORED.hi → AUTHORED.en
 */
